=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n油脂同肉梅花間竹分布<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肥膏位食落都唔覺得噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唐揚雞是即叫即炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉質好嫩 炸皮係厚咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個前列腺好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好 讚完啦 宜家要屌吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上我每次叫呢間自取<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次都至少要比我個預定自取時間再多幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日係比我個預定自取時間再等多3個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前可以當你岩岩開鋪sop未流暢要等耐啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家都開咗幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上個陣單仲未多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地真係要好好考慮吓接單出餐既sop要點行先順<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c529fbfe59c0f95fc187d279fe42731ede4197","tid":2174662,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"85c7ba050e986d763a7871eec18dc1d3c41c4bdb","tid":2174662,"uid":14409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"識食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:35:58.000Z","msg":"識食師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4146fab333be71c5894f495ce51d79486e30ed9f","tid":2174662,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"黃食師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />JGBU AGAIN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da257cb19f1da248f77c147